Package: divDyn
Type: Package
Title: Calculating metrics of diversity dynamics using occurrence data
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Adam T. Kocsis, Carl J. Reddin, John Alroy, Wolfgang Kiessling
Maintainer: Adam T. Kocsis <adamkocsis@fau.de>
Description: The package implements functions to describe sampling and diversity dynamics of fossil occurrence datasets (e.g. from the Paleobiology Database).
